literals: "Returns a full concatenated message for the test results and its inner result to the target max depth, only giving messages worse or equal to the provided severity level."
"The TestResult to give the full message for."
"Maximum level of recursiveness for inner TestInformation."
"The minimum level of severity of the information to report back."
comments: Return an empty string if the status is not at least as severe as the provided minimum.
Add messages from inner testresults that match the severity level.
